title: Episode 515 | "Work In Progress"
description:
Joe begins with letting people know that it's acceptable to be comfortable with yourself (11:50). Joe highlights the trend of artist evolving in music (37:00), Lil Durk and NBA Youngboy's tension (1:35:00), the return of music festivals (1:44:00), Morris Day & the time (2:20:05) and MORE!
